'''迎风坡'''是[[山|山]]或[[島嶼|岛屿]]迎着[[風|气流]]来向的一侧[[山坡地|坡]]。风向是北风时，则迎风坡是山的北坡。迎风坡降水通常比[[背风坡|背风坡]]多，如[[台湾|台湾]]东北部的迎风坡常遭遇[[强降水过程|强降水]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Orographic effects on heavy rainfall events over northeastern Taiwan during the northeasterly monsoon season|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0169809512003341|date=2013-03-01|journal=Atmospheric Research|doi=10.1016/j.atmosres.2012.10.008|volume=122|pages=310–335|language=en|issn=0169-8095}}</ref>。<ref name="NOAA">{{Cite web|title=What do leeward and windward mean?|url=https://oceanservice.noaa.gov/facts/windward-leeward.html|accessdate=November 3, 2020|publisher=NOAA}}</ref> 因为迎风坡的降水比背风坡多，[[水循环|水循环]]更活跃，更易积雪，故迎风坡[[雪线|雪线]]分布的[[海拔|海拔]]比背风坡低。迎风坡自然条件更为优越，人口、城镇分布较密集，所以[[经济|经济]]较发达。<ref>{{Cite book|title=自然地理学|first=光和|publisher=[[高等教育出版社|高等教育]]|year=2007|last=伍|last2=王|first2=乃昂|first3=双熙|last3=胡}}</ref>

